{"tid":2122700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：口罩是新冷戰的反共象徵物！","createTime":"2020-07-24T06:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T14:50:56.000Z","uid":108359,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ae1cd6bdf3763fa7fac7b97d0c4df8fb305e707f","tid":2122700,"uid":108359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"陳雲：口罩是新冷戰的反共象徵物！龐佩奧在今晨的演講中，特別談到口罩。他說中國隱瞞瘟疫，連累他們要戴口罩！這是特朗普總統在日前忽然在公開場合全隊人戴口罩的政治玄機！（之前之後他都無戴口罩）<br />\n在西方，戴口罩是埋怨中國、仇恨中國散播疫病的外在行為。口罩是新冷戰的象徵物！<br />\n現在我終於明白，為何香港特區政府要制定口罩強制令，因為要香港人齊心記住仇恨！醫學權威證明，健康人戴口罩根本毫無保護作用，而且帶來的感染弊病及呼吸道損害更多。<br />\n香港的泛民港獨，原來一直都是配合香港政府的號召，令全民反華反共的。"},{"pid":"40727207f03824823b5e5f8294adec38c4b909a4","tid":2122700,"uid":108359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d4448917e509a40942c14148fb34f9a1b151ca","tid":2122700,"uid":48631,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"戴口罩=反共<br />\n國師叫人唔好戴口罩<br />\n國師=唔反共"},{"pid":"8145e8d2248ce18fd73761b4f09704d706376b1a","tid":2122700,"uid":89030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老師又轉"},{"pid":"af7a1caebd567ba80ef6516eeb5b216180b88518","tid":2122700,"uid":9,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:53:10.000Z","msg":"咁陳雲係咪要戴口罩啦?"},{"pid":"824e1760866f9716c3bbcc6ecb93804644c61cb2","tid":2122700,"uid":76603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"熱狗精神病？"},{"pid":"3c39d9e1f5c4586fd2689f0f521ddd17a6974b7f","tid":2122700,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"